BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:DQoZmO9ZrQlCUk3ZzMsIp
SUMMARY:Trans Rights and Bodily Autonomy - Robert’s Rules Training
DTSTAMP:20260407T043752Z
DTSTART:20260407T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Trans Rights and Bodily Autonomy Working Group is holding a
	 training on Robert’s Rules of Order Newly Revised (RONR) as we work towar
	ds more structured meetings. \\nThis is a great opportunity for members ne
	w and old to learn the essentials of RONR—the parliamentary procedure used
	 across Seattle DSA. We’ll discuss how these rules specifically apply to w
	orking group meetings and have time for questions. \\nOnce the training is
	 over we’ll jump straight into our Biweekly Meeting where everyone can pra
	ctice their parliamentary prowess If you’d like to attend\\\, please regis
	ter for the regular meeting and arrive online on Signal by 7:30pm. \\nAll 
	DSA members are more than welcome to attend this training.\n\nhttps://seat
	tledsa.org/event/trans-rights-and-bodily-autonomy-roberts-rules-training/\
	n\nFrom Seattle DSA
