	 \\nSaturdays in South Seattle:\\n-Cooking shift: 1:30-4pm in Tukwila\\n-S
	erving shift: 4:30-7pm at Cafe Red (across the street from the light rail 
	station) \\nTo volunteer for a cooking or serving shift\\\, follow the ins
	tructions here. \\nWe are also looking for financial supporters. It costs 
	just $2 to feed a hungry neighbor. Support here!\n\nhttps://seattledsa.org
	/event/solidarity-dinner-south-seattle/2026-05-02/\n\nFrom Seattle DSA
