UID:I_v4hPHALpKzR2mCOPny5
SUMMARY:Pride Month Planning Meeting
DTSTAMP:20260407T043752Z
DTSTART:20260517T110000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle DSA is gearing up for Pride Month 2026! Comrades from s
	everal working groups and committees have come together to prepare for tab
	ling at events like Trans Pride Seattle and to host our own DSA Pride Even
	t. If you’d like to get involved in these efforts please join us for our b
